    <item>
      <title>梅尔斯说，德国为欧洲国防推动基金会奠定了基金会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/merz-says-germany-laying-foundation-for-european-defense-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[列在等待的总理弗里德里希·梅尔斯（Friedrich Merz）表示，德国向军事支出中解锁数十亿欧元的举动应被视为建立一个广阔的欧洲国防部，包括英国和挪威等非欧盟国家的“第一大步”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/merz-says-germany-laying-foundation-for-european-defense-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 09:57:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列以罢工结束加沙停战，将哈马斯归咎于崩溃</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/israel-say-it-s-launching-strikes-on-hamas-targets-in-gaza</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列在加沙横跨加沙的一夜之间发动了空袭，哈马斯说，数百人杀死了数百人，与巴勒斯坦集团打破了将近两个月的停火。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/israel-say-it-s-launching-strikes-on-hamas-targets-in-gaza</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 00:41:02 GMT</pubDate>
